<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="atmosphere-n">atmosphere <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'ætməsfɪə(r)/    美 /'ætməsfɪr/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 大气层；气体；空气：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The waste the factories create goes into <strong>the atmosphere</strong> and makes us sick.
工厂产生的废气进入大气中，导致我们生病。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a smoky atmosphere 
烟雾弥漫的空气</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 气氛；环境：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His appearance created an <strong>atmosphere of</strong> tension.
他的出现使气氛紧张起来。</p><footer>2014 湖北</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The top leaders of the two countries are holding talks in a friendly <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (气氛).  （2008 湖北改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. atmosphere  </p></div>